snippet.title: Magic: The Gathering Arena – By Fans, For Fans
snippet.description: The developers of Magic: The Gathering Arena want to show you what kind of players we are and why we are building MTG Arena for you. Sign up for the Closed Beta at PlayMTGArena.com
